OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain, which
OL,7,Fwill be mostly light. Remaining cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight but becoming dry with just a
OL,9,Ffew lingering outbreaks of light rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with just
OL,12,Fa few outbreaks of light rain
OL,13,Fpossible. Becoming brighter and
OL,14,Flargely dry during the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,17,Fcloudy, patchy rain on Tuesday, some
OL,18,Fbright spells. Wednesday and Thursday
OL,19,Fwill be dry with sunny spells and
OL,20,Fbecoming very warm.
